\par APF is activated, the regular I.F. SHIFT setting, if any,  is \'d2frozen,\'d3 
\par and SHIFT then controls the center pitch of the APF filter in 5-Hz
\par steps. APF is independent for the main and sub receivers, as well
\par as for presets I and II. Switching between these two presets is a 
\par convenient way of turning APF on/off quickly.
