 SWR <= 2.0:1
\par   }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f37\insrsid3036935 Medium-high pitch:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\insrsid3036935  SWR <= 3.0:1
