\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\fs22\insrsid3036935 
\par This feature was added primarily for our blind customers, but it\rquote s useful
\par whenever you tap ATU TUNE without looking at the final SWR reading.
