\par This is a major firmware release with a number of new features, including:
\par 
\par - Band independence for the sub receiver
\par - New AGC features especially for use in pileups
\par - ATU storage of multiple settings on each band, and per-antenna auto/bypass
\par - \'d2Birdie\'d3 removal menu entry
