{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}SPLIT{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} operation is possible 
\par with any combination of CW and SSB for VFO A and B. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af37\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f37\fs22\insrsid3036935 Same-mode}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\fs22\insrsid3036935  {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname State}}
