\par     during normal speech. If you\rquote re using an external peak-reading wattmeter or power 
\par     amplifier, adjust POWER as required while observing the effect of speech peaks.
\par     If you find that an SSB power setting higher or lower than for CW is often required,
\par     you may wish to compensate for this using the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\ai\af37\afs20 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\i\f37\fs20\insrsid3036935 CONFIG:TXG VCE}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af37\afs20 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f37\fs20\insrsid3036935  menu entry.
